dct_title_s: Hangzhou shi jiao tong jian tu.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Includes sketch map of Hangzhou. Tables of bus lines and stations, old and new street names, ill., and music on verso. Title translation: [Simplified transportation map of Hangzhou]. Inset: Hangzhou Shi lue tu [Sketch map of Hangzhou]. Index on verso.
dct_creator_sm: Zhejiang ren min chu ban she
dct_publisher_sm: [Hangzhou, China?] : Zhejiang ren min chu ban she, 1971.
